Package org.apache.axis.deployment

Interface Summary
DeployableItem Interface representing a Handler-derived object that is deployable into the Axis Deployment Registry
DeploymentDocument Represents a deployment descriptor document of some sort
 

Class Summary
DeploymentRegistry The DeploymentRegistry abstract class takes the place of the org.apache.axis.registry.HandlerRegistry and extends the functionality to cover all Axis deployable items.
 

Exception Summary
DeploymentException
